{"tid":123583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人生於世上有幾個知己 多少友誼能長存","createTime":"2017-02-17T03:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T15:13:28.000Z","uid":41411,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"812099d7bfc53d1323c663df53dabad70c0b777a","tid":123583,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:11:23.000Z","msg":"今日別離共你雙雙兩握手 友誼常在你我心裡<br />\n今天且有暫別　他朝也定能聚首　縱使不能會面　始終也是朋友　說有萬里山　隔阻兩地遙<br />\n不須見面　心中也知曉　友誼改不了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7742a8fa69ef182e1baa494fe0fc3d5bdd19be6","tid":123583,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7ce4ba381bbfd4d75a67040622b7aa49681fb7","tid":123583,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:15:56.000Z","msg":"好撚賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbut<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee910f503c1490f5f2240b6ce84707e82008399","tid":123583,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:22:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbut<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631cf5aec309c2434bf0740e6b93a4bfadea2327","tid":123583,"uid":62314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:24:02.000Z","msg":"柒警！有人拜你山！"},{"pid":"45b2a95db0388c5de113124a83e12a7627df9cd7","tid":123583,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T07:38:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d409f92a2fef5